page.title: 20Durris Domesday Work Credits
page.content: This work forthe nationwide Domesday Project was planned,written and put on to computer file by the Primary 5,6 and 7 pupils of Woodlands School, Durris, with their Head Teacher Mr. Philip Benzie,during June 1985.The pupils were:P.5-Tommy Murphy,Emma Bannerman,Keith Benzie,Elaine Coutts, Derek Petrie and Christopher Stephen. P.6-Iain Gibson,Philip Ross,Vicky Bannerman,Susan Beattie,Corinna Abbott,Simon Smith,Caroline Stephen and Jennifer Petrie. P.7-Anna Moorhouse,Brian Murphy, Michael Coutts,Alison Donald,James Blackhall,Angela Beattie and Neil Gibson.
